				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Molto Espressivo Wins All Bard LDoN Mission, lvl 49 - 56<a name="21421"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 14 04 4:34 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>We bought Virtues before we went.  I suppose I would have had some closer shaves without the extra HPs.  Generally though, we only stopped to heal me up every 4 or 5 mobs or so.  I simply would have had to pause more frequently.
<br />

<br />
The other thing that we can always do is kite.  I did that for part of the time.  Basically snare-dragging the mob back and forth in a big room while I chanted on it, and the others smacked it.  Doing it that way, we can pretty much do it without getting hit hardly at all.  It was pretty annoying though, so I started standing toe to toe instead with drum and weapon offhand, chanting and smacking.
<br />

<br />
If anyone wants us to try it again without buffs to &quot;prove&quot; we can truly &quot;do it alone&quot;, I'm game.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
